{"type":"message","id":"9fb610ec","parentId":"744a4a5b","timestamp":"2026-03-03T03:58:02.058Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4d3d23a93f5b40d185fa9410","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"pages\": [\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"ZIP MCP Server is a compression server based on fastMCP and zip.js, offering parameter-controlled ZIP compression, decompression, and compressed package information query functions. TypeScriptLocal DeploymentFile CompressionData PackagingEncrypted CompressionMulti-file ProcessingMetadata Query B-Good Reliable functionality and a solid user experience. Some areas may still need improvement. Hide Details Validated for availability This MCP has been validated by the platform to ensure availability Installation method provided Supports1installation methods for easy deployment Easy Installation Available Provides installation options besides manual setup Practical Tools Included At least one tool for the service included Service license License: MIT License Agreement Service details provided Includes a detailed MCP introduction document Contains Prompts Provides prompt templates for interactive use Includes Resources Includes resources for managing context data ZIP MCP Server 中文| English Project Introduction ZIP MCP Server is a compression server based on fastMCP and zip.js, implementing the Model Context Protocol (MCP). This project provides fully parameter-controlled ZIP compression, decompression, and query compression package information functions. Features Supports compression and decompression of files and data Supports multi-file packaging compression Provides compression level control (0-9) Supports password protection and encryption strength settings Provides query function for compressed package metadata Project Structure BASH 12345678 zip-mcp├── src│ ├── index.ts # Application entry point│ ├── utils│ │ └── compression.ts # Compression and decompression implementation├── tsconfig.json # TypeScript configuration file├── package.json # npm configuration file└── README.md # Project documentation Installation You can install ZIP MCP Server globally using npm:\",\n      \"hostname\": \"\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://mcpworld.bdstatic.com/store/v2/d4f2bff/platform-openai/5ee511c/favicon.ico\",\n      \"title\": \"ZIP MCP Server - Efficient Compression and Decompression Solution - MCP Service\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.mcpworld.com/en/detail/689fa2ece2a1ecb302119d521235b2a3\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"点此即可享一键秒级部署。 OpenClaw一键部署curl.qcloud.com/OZhKMTQh 可视化面板快速接入QQ、企微、飞书、钉钉等IM应用,同时支持海外Discord、WhatsApp、Telegram、iMessage等应用。有了它,OpenClaw 就能直接玩转腾讯云对象存储(COS),像什么管文件、修图、智能搜图之类的活儿,统统不在话下! 可视化面板快速接入QQ、企微、飞书、钉钉等IM应用,同时支持海外Discord、WhatsApp、Telegram、iMessage等应用。 如果你不喜欢跟机器人对话安装,也能去Clawhub下个zip 包,手动解压到本地的 skill 文件夹里: 用Linux 的朋友,敲一行npx clawhub@latest install tencentcloud-cos也能搞定。 Windows 用户就直接下那个 zip 包,丢进本地 skill 目录就行。记得配权限的时候抠门点,给够用的就行,别全给了,安全第一。 可视化面板快速接入QQ、企微、飞书、钉钉等IM应用,同时支持海外Discord、WhatsApp、Telegram、iMessage等应用。 ✨ 核心功能🗂️ 玩转云存储传文件: 把本地文件扔进 COS 桶里下文件: 从 COS 把文件捞回本地看列表: 瞅瞅桶里都有啥管文件: 删、拷、挪,样样行🖼️ 搞定图片 (数据万象CI) 查信息: 看看图片的“身份证”评质量: 给图片打个分变高清: AI 帮你把糊图变清晰一键抠图: 自动把背景去了扫码: 读出图片里的二维码加水印: 给图片盖个章🔍 聪明搜图以图搜图: 拿张图找类似的文字搜图: 描述一下就能找到图📄 文档神器转格式: 各种文档转 PDF 搞视频: 自动截封面、抽帧\",\n      \"hostname\": \"知乎\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://ss1.baidu.com/6ONXsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=493147230,3096476255&fm=195&app=88&f=JPEG?w=200&h=200\",\n      \"title\": \"我用OpenClaw手搓了个网盘,下载速度贼快!\",\n      \"url\": \"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2009258266736223353\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"哦,我的mcp提供了以下工具: 📦 压缩(5个工具):具有安全功能的ZIP/TAR压缩和提取 🌐 Web和网络(18个工具):Web搜索、页面获取、HTML解析、下载、HTTP API客户端、DNS查找 📁 文件系统(12个工具):读取、写入、搜索文件和目录、文件比较 📊 数据处理(15个工具):JSON、CSV、XML、YAML、TOML解析和操作 📝 文本处理(9个工具):正则表达式、编码、电子邮件/URL提取、文本相似性 💻 系统(8个工具):系统信息、CPU/内存监控、环境变量 🛠️ 公用事业(10个工具):UUID、哈希、日期/时间操作、数学、密码生成 🤖 子代理AI(6个工具):将子任务委托给外部AI模型(OpenAI/Anthropic)、并行执行、条件分支、持久配置 🌐 浏览器自动化(33个工具):基于Selenium的浏览器控制、页面导航、元素交互、屏幕截图、JavaScript执行、多标签管理 注:Python开发、UV包管理器和Pylance/Pyright工具已从打包版本中删除,因为它们需要外部Python解释器和包管理器。所有剩余的工具完全独立工作。 📚 文档 📖 文档索引- Complete documentation hub (中文) 🏗️ 项目结构-详细的项目组织 🎯 安装指南-交互式配置向导指南 📦 构建指南-Windows/Linux发行版软件包 🏛️ 架构指南-系统架构与设计 🧪 子代理指南-AI编排功能 ⚡ 快速安装与配置 安装依赖并开发模式安装: BASH 1 pip install -e . 运行交互式配置向导(推荐): BASH 1 uv run configure.py 或直接为Claude Desktop生成配置: BASH 1 python -m mcp_server.cli.\",\n      \"hostname\": \"\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://mcpworld.bdstatic.com/store/v2/d4f2bff/platform-openai/5ee511c/favicon.ico\",\n      \"title\": \"多功能工具服务器\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.mcpworld.com/zh/detail/0cac1027b19ec51df7a73d83f998bb6c\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"已通过可用性验证 该MCP已经通过平台验证,确保可用  许可证:MIT协议  一种MCP服务器,通过自动将文件汇总到其公共接口来降低Claude上下文窗口成本。 当Claude跨多个文件处理大型任务时,上下文窗口会不断增长。 完成一个文件后,Claude不需要完整的实现,只需要公共接口(结构、函数、特征)。 此MCP服务器: 优雅地处理不支持的语言--返回完整内容,不进行跟踪 npx github:YOUR_USERNAME/mcp-file-compaction git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/mcp-file-compaction.gitcd mcp-file-compactionnpm installnpm run build {\\\"mcpServers\\\":{\\\"file-compaction\\\":{\\\"command\\\":\\\"npx\\\",\\\"args\\\":[\\\"github:YOUR_USERNAME/mcp-file-compaction\\\"]}}} 添加到您的 CLAUDE.md: MARKDOWN ## File OperationsUse the file-compaction MCP server for file operations:- `read_file` instead of `Read` when you need full file contents- `peek_file` when you only need to check interfaces- `edit_file` instead of `Edit` for modifications- `write_file` instead of `Write` for new files- `file_status` to see tracked files and context savingsThis reduces context window size by keeping only summaries of inactive files.\",\n      \"hostname\": \"\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://mcpworld.bdstatic.com/store/v2/d4f2bff/platform-openai/5ee511c/favicon.ico\",\n      \"title\": \"同时使用(4KB)→ 上下文:9KB\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.mcpworld.com/zh/detail/39ba76d75be311cd79e2afeb9a75ad62\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"而攻击者正是通过注册为ClawHub的开发者,之后开发并批量上传伪装成合法技能插件的恶意“Skills”,通过“ClickFix”模式的社工攻击技巧,诱导用户下载安装,在用户系统中植入运行恶意代码。构成了一起严重的面向AI生态的供应链投毒攻击事件。使用安天AVL SDK反病毒引擎的主机安全产品升级后均可检测拦截相关恶意Skills文件样本,及其关联下载的样本。目前已衍生出数千种各类Skills,涵盖自动化办公、加密货币工具、社交媒体辅助等多个场景,初步形成了自组织、快速演化的开源生态。2026年2月1日,国际安全团队Koi Security在ClawHub平台上发现大量恶意Skills集中植入,并将相关攻击称之为“ClawHavoc”攻击行动[1],我们尊重Koi率先发现者对事件的命名权,将攻击事件中文名译为“利爪浩劫”,同时根据投毒样本的形态特点,将相关批次样本命名为Trojan/OpenClaw.PolySkill。 ClawHub运营者已经进行了响应处理,部分恶意Skills已无法搜索到,但仍有“漏网之鱼”,在规模性下架恶意Skills后,截止到本报告发布时点,ClawHub平台中共包含3498个Skills。其中ID为hightower6eu的作者上传恶意包最多,达677个。相关风险如果不能有效遏止,也会制约OpenClaw开源生态的健康与可持续发展。\",\n      \"hostname\": \"哔哩哔哩弹幕网\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://b.bdstatic.com/searchbox/mappconsole/image/20181030/1540889038159862.png\",\n      \"title\": \"利爪浩劫——面向AI代理OpenClaw技能市场的大规模投毒行动分析\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv45818851\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"request_id\": \"1c80d2ae-491a-4491-ade2-7fffb8b79738\",\n  \"tools\": [],\n  \"status\": 0\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5040,"aggregated":"{\n  \"pages\": [\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"ZIP MCP Server is a compression server based on fastMCP and zip.js, offering parameter-controlled ZIP compression, decompression, and compressed package information query functions. TypeScriptLocal DeploymentFile CompressionData PackagingEncrypted CompressionMulti-file ProcessingMetadata Query B-Good Reliable functionality and a solid user experience. Some areas may still need improvement. Hide Details Validated for availability This MCP has been validated by the platform to ensure availability Installation method provided Supports1installation methods for easy deployment Easy Installation Available Provides installation options besides manual setup Practical Tools Included At least one tool for the service included Service license License: MIT License Agreement Service details provided Includes a detailed MCP introduction document Contains Prompts Provides prompt templates for interactive use Includes Resources Includes resources for managing context data ZIP MCP Server 中文| English Project Introduction ZIP MCP Server is a compression server based on fastMCP and zip.js, implementing the Model Context Protocol (MCP). This project provides fully parameter-controlled ZIP compression, decompression, and query compression package information functions. Features Supports compression and decompression of files and data Supports multi-file packaging compression Provides compression level control (0-9) Supports password protection and encryption strength settings Provides query function for compressed package metadata Project Structure BASH 12345678 zip-mcp├── src│ ├── index.ts # Application entry point│ ├── utils│ │ └── compression.ts # Compression and decompression implementation├── tsconfig.json # TypeScript configuration file├── package.json # npm configuration file└── README.md # Project documentation Installation You can install ZIP MCP Server globally using npm:\",\n      \"hostname\": \"\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://mcpworld.bdstatic.com/store/v2/d4f2bff/platform-openai/5ee511c/favicon.ico\",\n      \"title\": \"ZIP MCP Server - Efficient Compression and Decompression Solution - MCP Service\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.mcpworld.com/en/detail/689fa2ece2a1ecb302119d521235b2a3\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"点此即可享一键秒级部署。 OpenClaw一键部署curl.qcloud.com/OZhKMTQh 可视化面板快速接入QQ、企微、飞书、钉钉等IM应用,同时支持海外Discord、WhatsApp、Telegram、iMessage等应用。有了它,OpenClaw 就能直接玩转腾讯云对象存储(COS),像什么管文件、修图、智能搜图之类的活儿,统统不在话下! 可视化面板快速接入QQ、企微、飞书、钉钉等IM应用,同时支持海外Discord、WhatsApp、Telegram、iMessage等应用。 如果你不喜欢跟机器人对话安装,也能去Clawhub下个zip 包,手动解压到本地的 skill 文件夹里: 用Linux 的朋友,敲一行npx clawhub@latest install tencentcloud-cos也能搞定。 Windows 用户就直接下那个 zip 包,丢进本地 skill 目录就行。记得配权限的时候抠门点,给够用的就行,别全给了,安全第一。 可视化面板快速接入QQ、企微、飞书、钉钉等IM应用,同时支持海外Discord、WhatsApp、Telegram、iMessage等应用。 ✨ 核心功能🗂️ 玩转云存储传文件: 把本地文件扔进 COS 桶里下文件: 从 COS 把文件捞回本地看列表: 瞅瞅桶里都有啥管文件: 删、拷、挪,样样行🖼️ 搞定图片 (数据万象CI) 查信息: 看看图片的“身份证”评质量: 给图片打个分变高清: AI 帮你把糊图变清晰一键抠图: 自动把背景去了扫码: 读出图片里的二维码加水印: 给图片盖个章🔍 聪明搜图以图搜图: 拿张图找类似的文字搜图: 描述一下就能找到图📄 文档神器转格式: 各种文档转 PDF 搞视频: 自动截封面、抽帧\",\n      \"hostname\": \"知乎\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://ss1.baidu.com/6ONXsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=493147230,3096476255&fm=195&app=88&f=JPEG?w=200&h=200\",\n      \"title\": \"我用OpenClaw手搓了个网盘,下载速度贼快!\",\n      \"url\": \"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2009258266736223353\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"哦,我的mcp提供了以下工具: 📦 压缩(5个工具):具有安全功能的ZIP/TAR压缩和提取 🌐 Web和网络(18个工具):Web搜索、页面获取、HTML解析、下载、HTTP API客户端、DNS查找 📁 文件系统(12个工具):读取、写入、搜索文件和目录、文件比较 📊 数据处理(15个工具):JSON、CSV、XML、YAML、TOML解析和操作 📝 文本处理(9个工具):正则表达式、编码、电子邮件/URL提取、文本相似性 💻 系统(8个工具):系统信息、CPU/内存监控、环境变量 🛠️ 公用事业(10个工具):UUID、哈希、日期/时间操作、数学、密码生成 🤖 子代理AI(6个工具):将子任务委托给外部AI模型(OpenAI/Anthropic)、并行执行、条件分支、持久配置 🌐 浏览器自动化(33个工具):基于Selenium的浏览器控制、页面导航、元素交互、屏幕截图、JavaScript执行、多标签管理 注:Python开发、UV包管理器和Pylance/Pyright工具已从打包版本中删除,因为它们需要外部Python解释器和包管理器。所有剩余的工具完全独立工作。 📚 文档 📖 文档索引- Complete documentation hub (中文) 🏗️ 项目结构-详细的项目组织 🎯 安装指南-交互式配置向导指南 📦 构建指南-Windows/Linux发行版软件包 🏛️ 架构指南-系统架构与设计 🧪 子代理指南-AI编排功能 ⚡ 快速安装与配置 安装依赖并开发模式安装: BASH 1 pip install -e . 运行交互式配置向导(推荐): BASH 1 uv run configure.py 或直接为Claude Desktop生成配置: BASH 1 python -m mcp_server.cli.\",\n      \"hostname\": \"\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://mcpworld.bdstatic.com/store/v2/d4f2bff/platform-openai/5ee511c/favicon.ico\",\n      \"title\": \"多功能工具服务器\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.mcpworld.com/zh/detail/0cac1027b19ec51df7a73d83f998bb6c\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"已通过可用性验证 该MCP已经通过平台验证,确保可用  许可证:MIT协议  一种MCP服务器,通过自动将文件汇总到其公共接口来降低Claude上下文窗口成本。 当Claude跨多个文件处理大型任务时,上下文窗口会不断增长。 完成一个文件后,Claude不需要完整的实现,只需要公共接口(结构、函数、特征)。 此MCP服务器: 优雅地处理不支持的语言--返回完整内容,不进行跟踪 npx github:YOUR_USERNAME/mcp-file-compaction git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/mcp-file-compaction.gitcd mcp-file-compactionnpm installnpm run build {\\\"mcpServers\\\":{\\\"file-compaction\\\":{\\\"command\\\":\\\"npx\\\",\\\"args\\\":[\\\"github:YOUR_USERNAME/mcp-file-compaction\\\"]}}} 添加到您的 CLAUDE.md: MARKDOWN ## File OperationsUse the file-compaction MCP server for file operations:- `read_file` instead of `Read` when you need full file contents- `peek_file` when you only need to check interfaces- `edit_file` instead of `Edit` for modifications- `write_file` instead of `Write` for new files- `file_status` to see tracked files and context savingsThis reduces context window size by keeping only summaries of inactive files.\",\n      \"hostname\": \"\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://mcpworld.bdstatic.com/store/v2/d4f2bff/platform-openai/5ee511c/favicon.ico\",\n      \"title\": \"同时使用(4KB)→ 上下文:9KB\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.mcpworld.com/zh/detail/39ba76d75be311cd79e2afeb9a75ad62\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"snippet\": \"而攻击者正是通过注册为ClawHub的开发者,之后开发并批量上传伪装成合法技能插件的恶意“Skills”,通过“ClickFix”模式的社工攻击技巧,诱导用户下载安装,在用户系统中植入运行恶意代码。构成了一起严重的面向AI生态的供应链投毒攻击事件。使用安天AVL SDK反病毒引擎的主机安全产品升级后均可检测拦截相关恶意Skills文件样本,及其关联下载的样本。目前已衍生出数千种各类Skills,涵盖自动化办公、加密货币工具、社交媒体辅助等多个场景,初步形成了自组织、快速演化的开源生态。2026年2月1日,国际安全团队Koi Security在ClawHub平台上发现大量恶意Skills集中植入,并将相关攻击称之为“ClawHavoc”攻击行动[1],我们尊重Koi率先发现者对事件的命名权,将攻击事件中文名译为“利爪浩劫”,同时根据投毒样本的形态特点,将相关批次样本命名为Trojan/OpenClaw.PolySkill。 ClawHub运营者已经进行了响应处理,部分恶意Skills已无法搜索到,但仍有“漏网之鱼”,在规模性下架恶意Skills后,截止到本报告发布时点,ClawHub平台中共包含3498个Skills。其中ID为hightower6eu的作者上传恶意包最多,达677个。相关风险如果不能有效遏止,也会制约OpenClaw开源生态的健康与可持续发展。\",\n      \"hostname\": \"哔哩哔哩弹幕网\",\n      \"hostlogo\": \"https://b.bdstatic.com/searchbox/mappconsole/image/20181030/1540889038159862.png\",\n      \"title\": \"利爪浩劫——面向AI代理OpenClaw技能市场的大规模投毒行动分析\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv45818851\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"request_id\": \"1c80d2ae-491a-4491-ade2-7fffb8b79738\",\n  \"tools\": [],\n  \"status\": 0\n}","cwd":"D:\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772510282056}}
{"type":"message","id":"7ef11905","parentId":"9fb610ec","timestamp":"2026-03-03T03:58:10.852Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"搜索结果里第一个就是 ZIP MCP Server，正好是用户需要的解压压缩包的 MCP 工具，直接把信息告诉用户就行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"有！头儿你看这个：\n\n**ZIP MCP Server** — 专门处理压缩包的 MCP 服务器。\n\n功能：\n- ZIP 压缩和解压\n- 支持密码保护\n- 可以查压缩包里的文件信息\n- 支持多文件打包\n\n地址：https://www.mcpworld.com/en/detail/689fa2ece2a1ecb302119d521235b2a3\n\n还有个**多功能工具服务器**也带压缩功能（5 个压缩工具）：https://www.mcpworld.com/zh/detail/0cac1027b19ec51df7a73d83f998bb6c\n\n你要用哪个？我帮你配？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":86728,"output":217,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86945,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772510282058}}
