,\"username\":\"dylanc-anthropic\"},{\"ema\r\nil\":\"ben@anthropic.com\",\"username\":\"benjmann\"},{\"email\":\"nikhil@anthropic.com\",\"username\":\"nikhil-anthropic\"},{\"email\":\r\n\"ethan.langevin@anthropic.com\",\"username\":\"ejlangev-ant\"},{\"email\":\"jv@anthropic.com\",\"username\":\"jv-anthropic\"},{\"emai\r\nl\":\"ollie@anthropic.com\",\"username\":\"ollie-ant-2025\"},{\"email\":\"packy@anthropic.com\",\"username\":\"packy-anthropic\"},{\"em\r\nail\":\"noahz@anthropic.com\",\"username\":\"noahz-anthropic\"},{\"email\":\"sbidasaria@anthropic.com\",\"username\":\"sbidasaria\"},{\r\n\"email\":\"wolffiex@anthropic.com\",\"username\":\"wolffiex\"},{\"email\":\"kofman@gmail.com\",\"username\":\"igorkofman\"},{\"email\":\"\r\nf@anthropic.com\",\"username\":\"felixrieseberg-anthropic\"},{\"email\":\"joan@anthropic.com\",\"username\":\"joan-anthropic\"}],\"li\r\ncense\":\"MIT\",\"date\":\"2025-12-04T04:57:44.382Z\",\"links\":{\"npm\":\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@anthropic-ai/mcpb\"}}\r\n,\r\n����λ�� ��:1 �ַ�: 55\r\n+ ... pm search zip-mcp --json | Select-Object -First 10 | ConvertFrom-Json\r\n+                                                          ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : NotSpecified: (:) [ConvertFrom-Json], ArgumentException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : System.ArgumentException,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.ConvertFromJsonCommand\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"D:\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772510999103}}
{"type":"message","id":"d722a922","parentId":"5cdf0367","timestamp":"2026-03-03T04:10:02.903Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"npm search 返回了 zip-mcp 包的信息，但 PowerShell 处理 JSON 有编码问题。不过我看到了关键信息：zip-mcp 最新版本是 1.0.5，发布时间是 2026-02-20。让我试试用 npx 直接运行而不是全局安装，或者试试其他类似的 MCP 服务器。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看到 `zip-mcp` 了，最新版 1.0.5。让我试试用 npx 直接跑，不加 `-y`：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_835b15299ccf440dae14591a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"npx zip-mcp --help","workdir":"D:\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":103608,"output":236,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103844,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772510999107}}
